{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775839131122,"sessionID":"ses_287bea41dffenf5Mfoy4ngVGvb","part":{"id":"prt_d78416ff8001wiLdE1nVSFy13Y","messageID":"msg_d78415cf3001SW320aVqTrfU5x","sessionID":"ses_287bea41dffenf5Mfoy4ngVGvb","type":"tool","tool":"task","callID":"toolu_cb58a4ef09164a28853c76d2","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"description":"Explore agentcube CRD patterns","prompt":"Explore the agentcube project codebase to understand:\n1. The structure of pkg/apis module - what CRDs already exist\n2. Existing CRD type definitions patterns (how they're defined, what fields they have)\n3. Any existing AgentRuntime related code or designs\n4. The overall project structure\n\nFocus on finding:\n- pkg/apis directory structure\n- Existing CRD definitions (look for *_types.go files)\n- Any design documents or specs related to AgentRuntime\n- Kubernetes CRD conventions used in this project\n\nReturn a summary of:\n- Current CRD types in pkg/apis\n- The pattern used for defining CRDs\n- Any existing AgentRuntime references\n- Recommended structure for AR-001 AgentRuntime CRD","subagent_type":"explore"},"output":"task_id: ses_287be841affemI68d5KH0ZqHio (for resuming to continue this task if needed)\n\n<task_result>\nBased on my exploration of the agentcube project codebase, here is a comprehensive summary:\n\n---\n\n## Summary: AgentCube CRD Structure and Patterns\n\n### 1. Current Project Structure\n\nThe agentcube project is organized into multiple modules:\n\n```\nagentcube/\n├── sandbox-orchestration/     # Core sandbox management\n│   ├── AR-005-sandbox-creation-processor/\n│   ├── design.md              # Sandbox orchestration design\n│   └── spec.md                # Detailed specs\n├── session-routing/           # Session routing component\n├── session-store/             # Session persistence\n├── deployment/                # Deployment configs\n├── changes/AR-001/            # AR-001 change specification\n├── design.md                  # AR-001 design (AgentRuntime CRD)\n└── proposal.md                # AR-001 proposal\n```\n\n**Note:** This is primarily a **design/proposal repository** - there are no actual Go implementation files (no `*.go` files found). The project exists as design documents and specifications.\n\n---\n\n### 2. Current CRD Types (Proposed in pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1)\n\nThe AR-001 design proposes **two CRDs** in the `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh` group:\n\n#### **AgentRuntime CRD**\n| Field | Type | Required | Default |\n|-------|------|----------|---------|\n| `maxSessionDuration` | `*metav1.Duration` | Yes | `\"8h\"` |\n| `sessionTimeout` | `*metav1.Duration` | Yes | `\"15m\"` |\n| `targetPort` | `[]TargetPort` | Yes | - |\n| `podTemplate` | `*PodTemplateSpec` | No | - |\n\n**Status:** `conditions []metav1.Condition`, `observedGeneration int64`\n\n#### **CodeInterpreter CRD**\n| Field | Type | Required | Default |\n|-------|------|----------|---------|\n| `authMode` | `AuthMode` (enum) | No | `\"picod\"` |\n| `maxSessionDuration` | `*metav1.Duration` | No | `\"8h\"` |\n| `sessionTimeout` | `*metav1.Duration` | No | `\"15m\"` |\n| `ports` | `[]TargetPort` | No | - |\n| `template` | `ContainerTemplateSpec` | Yes | - |\n| `warmPoolSize` | `*int32` | No | `0` |\n\n**Status:** `conditions`, `observedGeneration`, `ready bool`\n\n---\n\n### 3. CRD Definition Pattern Used\n\nThe project uses **kubebuilder/controller-gen** pattern with these conventions:\n\n#### File Structure:\n```\npkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/\n├── doc.go                    # Package docs + kubebuilder markers\n├── groupversion_info.go      # GroupVersion, SchemeBuilder\n├── register.go               # Kind constants, resource helpers  \n├── types.go                  # AgentRuntime and CodeInterpreter types\n└── zz_generated.deepcopy.go  # Generated (via controller-gen)\n```\n\n#### Kubebuilder Markers Used:\n```go\n// +genclient                           // Generate client\n// +k8s:deepcopy-gen:interfaces=...    // DeepCopy interfaces\n// +kubebuilder:object:root=true        // List type needed\n// +kubebuilder:subresource:status      // Status subresource\n// +kubebuilder:resource:scope=Namespaced\n// +kubebuilder:printcolumn:name=\"Age\",type=\"date\",JSONPath=\".metadata.creationTimestamp\"\n// +kubebuilder:validation:Required     // Required field\n// +kubebuilder:default=\"value\"         // Default value\n// +kubebuilder:validation:Enum=a;b     // Enum validation\n```\n\n#### API Group/Version:\n- **Group:** `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh`\n- **Version:** `v1alpha1`\n- **Resources:** `agentruntimes`, `codeinterpreters` (Namespaced)\n\n---\n\n### 4. Shared Types\n\n```go\n// TargetPort - Port configuration\ntype TargetPort struct {\n    Port        uint32       `json:\"port\"`\n    Protocol    ProtocolType `json:\"protocol\"`  // HTTP/HTTPS\n    Name        string       `json:\"name,omitempty\"`\n    PathPrefix  string       `json:\"pathPrefix,omitempty\"`\n}\n\n// PodTemplateSpec - Custom pod template (selective fields)\ntype PodTemplateSpec struct {\n    metav1.ObjectMeta\n    Spec corev1.PodSpec  // Embedded PodSpec\n}\n\n// ContainerTemplateSpec - Container spec for CodeInterpreter\ntype ContainerTemplateSpec struct {\n    Image            string\n    Command          []string\n    Args             []string\n    Env              []corev1.EnvVar\n    Resources        *corev1.ResourceRequirements\n    RuntimeClassName *string\n}\n\n// AuthMode - Enum type\ntype AuthModeType string\nconst (\n    AuthModePicoD AuthModeType = \"picod\"\n    AuthModeNone  AuthModeType = \"none\"\n)\n```\n\n---\n\n### 5. Existing AgentRuntime References\n\nThe design documents include references to how AgentRuntime is used:\n\n- **GVR (GroupVersionResource):**\n  ```go\n  AgentRuntimeGVR = schema.GroupVersionResource{\n      Group: \"runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh\", \n      Version: \"v1alpha1\", \n      Resource: \"agentruntimes\",\n  }\n  ```\n\n- **Workload Manager Integration:** AgentRuntime CRD is used by the workload manager to create/manage sandbox sessions\n\n- **Label Keys Used:**\n  - `runtime.agentcube.io/session-id`\n  - `runtime.agentcube.io/workload-name`\n  - `runtime.agentcube.io/sandbox-name`\n\n---\n\n### 6. Recommended AR-001 AgentRuntime CRD Structure\n\nBased on the design documents, here's the recommended structure:\n\n```\npkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/\n├── doc.go                           # Package with +groupName marker\n├── groupversion_info.go             # GroupVersion = runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1\n├── register.go                      # Kind constants\n├── agentruntime_types.go            # AgentRuntime + AgentRuntimeList\n├── codeinterpreter_types.go         # CodeInterpreter + CodeInterpreterList + shared types\n└── zz_generated.deepcopy.go         # Generated\n```\n\n**Key Files to Create:**\n\n1. **doc.go** - Package-level kubebuilder markers\n2. **groupversion_info.go** - SchemeBuilder and GroupVersion\n3. **register.go** - Kind constants, Resource() helper\n4. **agentruntime_types.go** - AgentRuntime, AgentRuntimeSpec, AgentRuntimeStatus, AgentRuntimeList\n5. **codeinterpreter_types.go** - CodeInterpreter, CodeInterpreterSpec, CodeInterpreterStatus, CodeInterpreterList, TargetPort, PodTemplateSpec, ContainerTemplateSpec, AuthModeType\n\n---\n\n### 7. Dependencies\n\n| Package | Version | Purpose |\n|---------|---------|---------|\n| `k8s.io/api/core/v1` | ^1.32 | PodSpec, core types |\n| `k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/apis/meta/v1` | ^1.32 | ObjectMeta, TypeMeta, conditions |\n| `k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/runtime` | ^1.32 | Scheme, runtime.Object |\n| `sigs.k8s.io/controller-tools/pkg/runtime` | ^0.17.2 | controller-gen markers |\n| `sigs.k8s.io/controller-tools/pkg/crd` | ^0.17.2 | CRD generation |\n</task_result>","metadata":{"sessionId":"ses_287be841affemI68d5KH0ZqHio","model":{"modelID":"MiniMax-M2.5","providerID":"bailian-coding-plan"},"truncated":false},"title":"Explore agentcube CRD patterns","time":{"start":1775839050722,"end":1775839131120}}}}
