{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775839153702,"sessionID":"ses_287bea41dffenf5Mfoy4ngVGvb","part":{"id":"prt_d7842c95d001NoKXQrbbYdAgKt","messageID":"msg_d7842b63c001w72TJ764G9u7RN","sessionID":"ses_287bea41dffenf5Mfoy4ngVGvb","type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"toolu_d98ab0aa159a499b87805fac","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"content":"# AR-001: CRD AgentRuntime 类型定义\n\n**Module:** pkg/apis  \n**Language:** Go  \n**Size:** S\n\n---\n\n## 任务清单\n\n### 阶段 1: 项目结构与基础文件\n\n- [ ] **T-001** 创建 `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/` 目录结构\n- [ ] **T-002** 创建 `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/doc.go` - 包文档与 kubebuilder markers\n- [ ] **T-003** 创建 `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/groupversion_info.go` - GroupVersion 与 SchemeBuilder\n- [ ] **T-004** 创建 `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/register.go` - Kind 常量与 Resource 辅助函数\n\n### 阶段 2: 共享类型定义\n\n- [ ] **T-005** 定义 `ProtocolType` 枚举类型 (HTTP/HTTPS)\n- [ ] **T-006** 定义 `TargetPort` 结构体\n- [ ] **T-007** 定义 `PodTemplateSpec` 结构体\n- [ ] **T-008** 验证共享类型单元测试通过\n\n### 阶段 3: AgentRuntime CRD 类型\n\n- [ ] **T-009** 创建 `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/agentruntime_types.go`\n- [ ] **T-010** 定义 `AgentRuntimeSpec` - maxSessionDuration, sessionTimeout, targetPort, podTemplate\n- [ ] **T-011** 定义 `AgentRuntimeStatus` - conditions, observedGeneration\n- [ ] **T-012** 定义 `AgentRuntime` CRD 类型 (包含 kubebuilder markers)\n- [ ] **T-013** 定义 `AgentRuntimeList` 列表类型\n- [ ] **T-014** 验证 AgentRuntime 类型编译通过\n\n### 阶段 4: CodeInterpreter CRD 类型 (可选/后续)\n\n- [ ] **T-015** 定义 `AuthModeType` 枚举 (picod/none)\n- [ ] **T-016** 定义 `ContainerTemplateSpec` 结构体\n- [ ] **T-017** 定义 `CodeInterpreterSpec`, `CodeInterpreterStatus`\n- [ ] **T-018** 定义 `CodeInterpreter` 与 `CodeInterpreterList` 类型\n\n### 阶段 5: 代码生成\n\n- [ ] **T-019** 运行 controller-gen 生成 `zz_generated.deepcopy.go`\n- [ ] **T-020** 运行 controller-gen 生成 CRD YAML (optional)\n- [ ] **T-021** 验证生成的 deepcopy 代码编译通过\n\n### 阶段 6: 验证与集成\n\n- [ ] **T-022** 注册 runtime scheme 到全局 schema\n- [ ] **T-023** 运行 `go build` 验证 pkg/apis 模块\n- [ ] **T-024** 运行 `go vet` 无警告\n- [ ] **T-025** 代码审查通过\n\n---\n\n## 依赖关系\n\n```\nT-001 ─┬─ T-002 ─ T-003 ─ T-004\n       │\n       └─ T-005 ─ T-006 ─ T-007 ─ T-008\n               │\n               └─ T-009 ─ T-010 ─ T-011 ─ T-012 ─ T-013 ─ T-014\n                       │\n                       └─ T-015 ─ T-016 ─ T-017 ─ T-018\n                               │\n                               └─ T-019 ─ T-020 ─ T-021 ─ T-022 ─ T-023 ─ T-024 ─ T-025\n```\n\n## 验收标准\n\n- [ ] `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/` 目录包含所有类型定义文件\n- [ ] AgentRuntime CRD 包含 spec: maxSessionDuration, sessionTimeout, targetPort, podTemplate\n- [ ] AgentRuntime CRD 包含 status: conditions, observedGeneration\n- [ ] 所有类型实现 `runtime.Object` 接口\n- [ ] 生成 deepcopy 方法\n- [ ] go build / go vet 通过","filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/tasks.md"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{},"filepath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/tasks.md","exists":false,"truncated":false},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/tasks.md","time":{"start":1775839153691,"end":1775839153700}}}}
